trans-unit.source: Represents the parameters used to invoke a compiler.
trans-unit.target: Representerer parametere som brukes til å starte en kompilator.

trans-unit.source: A CompilerParameters object represents the settings and options for an <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.ICodeCompiler> interface.
trans-unit.target: Et objekt for CompilerParameters representerer innstillingene og alternativer for en <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.ICodeCompiler>grensesnittet.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.ICodeCompiler>

trans-unit.source: If you are compiling an executable program, you must set the <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.GenerateExecutable%2A> property to `true`.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du kompilerer et kjørbart program, må du angi den <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.GenerateExecutable%2A>egenskapen `true`.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.GenerateExecutable%2A>

trans-unit.source: When the <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.GenerateExecutable%2A> is set to `false`, the compiler will generate a class library.
trans-unit.target: Når den <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.GenerateExecutable%2A>er satt til `false`, kompilatoren genererer et klassebibliotek.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.GenerateExecutable%2A>

trans-unit.source: By default, a new CompilerParameters is initialized with its <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.GenerateExecutable%2A> property set to `false`.
trans-unit.target: Som standard en ny CompilerParameters er initialisert med den <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.GenerateExecutable%2A>-egenskapen satt til `false`.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.GenerateExecutable%2A>

trans-unit.source: If you are compiling an executable from a CodeDOM graph, a <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeEntryPointMethod> must be defined in the graph.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du kompilerer et kjørbart program fra en CodeDOM diagrammet en <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeEntryPointMethod>må være definert i diagrammet.</xref:System.CodeDom.CodeEntryPointMethod>

trans-unit.source: If there are multiple code entry points, you can indicate the class that defines the entry point to use by setting the name of the class to the <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.MainClass%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Hvis det finnes flere kodepunktene oppføring, kan du angi klassen som definerer inngangspunktet skal brukes ved å angi navnet på klassen til den <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.MainClass%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.MainClass%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can specify a file name for the output assembly in the <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.OutputAssembly%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Du kan angi et filnavn for output-samlingen i den <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.OutputAssembly%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.OutputAssembly%2A>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, a default output file name will be used.
trans-unit.target: Ellers brukes et filnavn for standard utdata.

trans-unit.source: To include debug information in a generated assembly, set the <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.IncludeDebugInformation%2A> property to `true`.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil inkludere feilsøkingsinformasjon i en generert samling, kan du angi den <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.IncludeDebugInformation%2A>egenskapen `true`.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.IncludeDebugInformation%2A>

trans-unit.source: If your project references any assemblies, you must specify the assembly names as items in a <xref:System.Collections.Specialized.StringCollection> set to the <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.ReferencedAssemblies%2A> property of the CompilerParameters used when invoking compilation.
trans-unit.target: Hvis prosjektet refererer til alle samlinger, må du angi navn på samlinger som elementer i en <xref:System.Collections.Specialized.StringCollection>satt til den <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.ReferencedAssemblies%2A>for CompilerParameters brukes ved aktivering av kompileringsfeil.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.ReferencedAssemblies%2A> </xref:System.Collections.Specialized.StringCollection>

trans-unit.source: You can compile an assembly that is written to memory rather than disk by setting the <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.GenerateInMemory%2A> property to `true`.
trans-unit.target: Du kan kompileres en samling som er skrevet til minne i stedet for disk ved å angi den <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.GenerateInMemory%2A>egenskapen `true`.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.GenerateInMemory%2A>

trans-unit.source: When an assembly is generated in memory, your code can obtain a reference to the generated assembly from the <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerResults.CompiledAssembly%2A> property of a <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerResults>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis en samling genereres i minnet, kan koden hente en referanse til samlingen generert fra <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerResults.CompiledAssembly%2A>egenskapen for <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerResults>.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerResults> </xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerResults.CompiledAssembly%2A>

trans-unit.source: If an assembly is written to disk, you can obtain the path to the generated assembly from the <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerResults.PathToAssembly%2A> property of a <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerResults>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis en samling skrives til disken, kan du hente banen til genererte samlingen fra <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerResults.PathToAssembly%2A>egenskapen for <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerResults>.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerResults> </xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerResults.PathToAssembly%2A>

trans-unit.source: To specify a warning level at which to halt compilation, set the <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.WarningLevel%2A> property to an integer that represents the warning level at which to halt compilation.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil angi en advarselsnivå vil stoppe kompilering, angitt av <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.WarningLevel%2A>til et heltall som representerer advarsel vil stoppe kompilering.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.WarningLevel%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can also configure the compiler to halt compilation if warnings are encountered by setting the <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.TreatWarningsAsErrors%2A> property to `true`.
trans-unit.target: Du kan også konfigurere kompilator for å stoppe kompilering Hvis det oppstår advarsler ved å angi den <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.TreatWarningsAsErrors%2A>egenskapen `true`.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.TreatWarningsAsErrors%2A>

trans-unit.source: To specify a custom command-line arguments string to use when invoking the compilation process, set the string in the <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.CompilerOptions%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil angi en egendefinert kommandolinjeargumenter strengen som skal brukes ved aktivering av kompilering prosessen, kan du angi strengen i den <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.CompilerOptions%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.CompilerOptions%2A>

trans-unit.source: If a Win32 security token is required to invoke the compiler process, specify the token in the <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.UserToken%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Hvis en sikkerhetskode for Win32 kreves for å aktivere kompilatoren prosessen, kan du angi token i den <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.UserToken%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.UserToken%2A>

trans-unit.source: To include .NET Framework resource files in the compiled assembly, add the names of the resource files to the <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.EmbeddedResources%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil inkludere .NET Framework ressursfiler i kompilert samling, kan du legge til navnene på ressursfiler til den <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.EmbeddedResources%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.EmbeddedResources%2A>

trans-unit.source: To reference .NET Framework resources in another assembly, add the names of the resource files to the <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.LinkedResources%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: En referanse til .NET Framework-ressurser i en annen samling, kan du legge til navnene på ressursfiler til den <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.LinkedResources%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.LinkedResources%2A>

trans-unit.source: To include a Win32 resource file in the compiled assembly, specify the name of the Win32 resource file in the <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.Win32Resource%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil inkludere en Win32-ressursfil i kompilerte samlingen, kan du angi navnet på Win32-ressursfilen i den <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.Win32Resource%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.Win32Resource%2A>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > This class contains a link demand and an inheritance demand at the class level that applies to all members.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Denne klassen inneholder en kobling behov, og en arv behov på klassen nivå som gjelder for alle medlemmer.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Security.SecurityException> is thrown when either the immediate caller or the derived class does not have full-trust permission.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Security.SecurityException>forårsakes når umiddelbar oppkalleren eller den utledede klassen ikke har tillatelse for fullstendig klarering.</xref:System.Security.SecurityException>

trans-unit.source: For details about security demands, see [Link Demands](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) and [Inheritance Demands](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/28b9adbb-8f08-4f10-b856-dbf59eb932d9).
trans-unit.target: For mer informasjon om krav for sikkerhet, kan du se [koblingen krav](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) og [arv krav](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/28b9adbb-8f08-4f10-b856-dbf59eb932d9).

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets optional command-line arguments to use when invoking the compiler.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir valgfrie kommandolinjeargumenter som skal brukes ved aktivering av kompilatoren.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.ICodeCompiler> typically includes this string on the command line when invoking a command-line compiler.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.ICodeCompiler>inneholder vanligvis denne strengen fra kommandolinjen ved aktivering av en kommandolinje kompilator.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.ICodeCompiler>

trans-unit.source: By default, this property contains an empty string.
trans-unit.target: Som standard inneholder denne egenskapen en tom streng.

trans-unit.source: Any additional command-line arguments for the compiler.
trans-unit.target: Noen ekstra kommandolinjeargumenter for kompilatoren.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the name of the core or standard assembly that contains basic types such as <xref:System.Object>, <xref:System.String>, or <xref:System.Int32>.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir navnet på kjerner eller standard samlingen som inneholder grunnleggende typer som <xref:System.Object>, <xref:System.String>, eller <xref:System.Int32>.</xref:System.Int32> </xref:System.String> </xref:System.Object>

trans-unit.source: If the value of this property is an empty string or `null`, the compiler uses the default core assembly.
trans-unit.target: Hvis verdien for denne egenskapen er en tom streng eller `null`, kompilatoren bruker standard kjerner samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Depending on the compiler version, the default core assembly may be mscorlib.dll or System.Runtime.dll in a Framework directory or reference assembly directory.
trans-unit.target: Avhengig av Kompilatorversjon kanskje kjerner standardsamling mscorlib.dll eller System.Runtime.dll i en Framework-katalog eller referanse samlingen katalog.

trans-unit.source: If the value of this property is not empty, the Code Document Object Model (CodeDOM) explicitly references the specified assembly and emits compiler options that cause the compiler to not reference any assemblies implicitly during compilation..
trans-unit.target: Hvis verdien for denne egenskapen er tom, refererer til den angitte samlingen kode dokumentobjektmodellen (CodeDOM) eksplisitt, og det avgir kompilatoren alternativer som forårsaker kompilatoren ikke referere til alle samlinger implisitt under kompilering..

trans-unit.source: For compilers that reference the core or standard assembly only implicitly by default, this property can be used on its own.
trans-unit.target: For kompilatorer som refererer til core eller standard samlingen bare implisitt ved standard, kan denne egenskapen brukes for seg selv.

trans-unit.source: For compilers that implicitly reference assemblies in addition to the core or standard assembly, using this option may require specifying additional entries in the <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.ReferencedAssemblies%2A?displayProperty=fullName>property.
trans-unit.target: For kompilatorer som implisitt refererer til samlinger i tillegg til core eller standard samling, ved hjelp av dette alternativet kan kreve at den angir flere oppføringer i den <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.ReferencedAssemblies%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.ReferencedAssemblies%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > An <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.ICodeCompiler> or <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider> implementation may choose to ignore this property.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > En <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.ICodeCompiler>eller <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider>implementering kan velge å ignorere denne egenskapen.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider> </xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.ICodeCompiler>

trans-unit.source: The name of the core assembly that contains basic types.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på kjerner samlingen som inneholder grunnleggende typer.

trans-unit.source: Gets the .NET Framework resource files to include when compiling the assembly output.
trans-unit.target: Henter .NET Framework-ressursfiler inkludere ved kompilering av samlingen utdataene.

trans-unit.source: Embedded resources are built into the generated assembly output file.
trans-unit.target: Innebygde ressurser er innebygd i utdatafilen generert samling.

trans-unit.source: Including files through this property is similar to the `/resource` command-line argument supported by many of the .NET Framework compilers.
trans-unit.target: Inkludert filer gjennom denne egenskapen er lik den `/resource` kommandolinjeargumenter som støttes av mange av .NET Framework-kompilatorer.

trans-unit.source: Not all compilers support .NET Framework resource files, so you should test for this support by calling the <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.ICodeGenerator.Supports%2A> method with the flag <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.GeneratorSupport>.
trans-unit.target: Ikke alle kompilatorer støtter ressursfiler for .NET Framework, slik at du skal teste dette ved å kalle <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.ICodeGenerator.Supports%2A>metoden med flagget <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.GeneratorSupport>.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.GeneratorSupport> </xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.ICodeGenerator.Supports%2A>

trans-unit.source: Add one or more .NET Framework resource file paths to the returned <xref:System.Collections.Specialized.StringCollection> to embed the file resources in the compiled assembly.
trans-unit.target: Legg til én eller flere .NET Framework ressursen filbaner det returnerte <xref:System.Collections.Specialized.StringCollection>til innebyggingsressurser filen i den kompilerte samlingen.</xref:System.Collections.Specialized.StringCollection>

trans-unit.source: Adding a duplicate or invalid file path results in compilation errors; ensure that each string specifies a unique path to a valid .NET Framework resource file.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du legger til en duplikat eller ugyldig bane, resulterer i kompileringsfeil; Kontroller at hver streng angir en unik bane til en gyldig .NET Framework-ressursfil.

trans-unit.source: Use EmbeddedResources to include default or neutral culture .NET Framework resources for an assembly; use the <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.LinkedResources%2A> property to reference .NET Framework resources in satellite assemblies.
trans-unit.target: Bruk EmbeddedResources til å inkludere standard eller nøytral kultur .NET Framework-ressurser for en samling; Bruk av <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.LinkedResources%2A>til å referere til .NET Framework-ressurser i satelittsamlingene.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.LinkedResources%2A>

trans-unit.source: A collection that contains the file paths of .NET Framework resources to include in the generated assembly.
trans-unit.target: En samling som inneholder filbaner av .NET Framework ressurser som skal inkluderes i generert samling.

trans-unit.source: Specifies an evidence object that represents the security policy permissions to grant the compiled assembly.
trans-unit.target: Angir et bevis-objekt som representerer sikkerhetstillatelser for policyen til å gi kompilerte samlingen.

trans-unit.source: An object that represents the security policy permissions to grant the compiled assembly.
trans-unit.target: Et objekt som representerer sikkerhetstillatelser for policyen til å gi kompilerte samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value indicating whether to generate an executable.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om du vil generere en kjørbar fil.

trans-unit.source: If the value of this property is `false`, a DLL will be generated.
trans-unit.target: Hvis verdien for denne egenskapen `false`, genereres det en DLL-fil.

trans-unit.source: By default, the value of this property is `false`.
trans-unit.target: Verdien for denne egenskapen er som standard `false`.

trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis kompilatoren skal generere utdataene i minnet; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value indicating whether to include debug information in the compiled executable.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om du vil inkludere feilsøkingsinformasjon i den kompilerte kjørbare filen.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if debug information should be generated; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis feilsøkingsinformasjon skal genereres; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets the .NET Framework resource files that are referenced in the current source.
trans-unit.target: Henter .NET Framework-ressursfiler som refereres til i den gjeldende kilden.

trans-unit.source: Linked resource files allow your assembly to reference .NET Framework resources without embedding the actual resources in the assembly.
trans-unit.target: Koblede ressursfiler tillater at samlingen referere til .NET Framework-ressurser uten å bygge de faktiske ressursene i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Referencing files through this property is similar to the `/linkresource` command-line argument supported by many of the .NET Framework compilers.
trans-unit.target: Refererer til filer gjennom denne egenskapen er lik den `/linkresource` kommandolinjeargumenter som støttes av mange av .NET Framework-kompilatorer.

trans-unit.source: Not all compilers support .NET Framework resource files, so you should test for this support by calling the <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.ICodeGenerator.Supports%2A> method with the flag <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.GeneratorSupport>.
trans-unit.target: Ikke alle kompilatorer støtter ressursfiler for .NET Framework, slik at du skal teste dette ved å kalle <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.ICodeGenerator.Supports%2A>metoden med flagget <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.GeneratorSupport>.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.GeneratorSupport> </xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.ICodeGenerator.Supports%2A>

trans-unit.source: Add one or more .NET Framework resource file paths to the returned <xref:System.Collections.Specialized.StringCollection> to create links for the resources in the compiled assembly.
trans-unit.target: Legg til én eller flere .NET Framework ressursen filbaner det returnerte <xref:System.Collections.Specialized.StringCollection>til å opprette koblinger for ressursene i kompilerte samlingen.</xref:System.Collections.Specialized.StringCollection>

trans-unit.source: Adding a duplicate or invalid file path results in compilation errors; ensure that each string specifies a unique path to a valid .NET Framework resource file.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du legger til en duplikat eller ugyldig bane, resulterer i kompileringsfeil; Kontroller at hver streng angir en unik bane til en gyldig .NET Framework-ressursfil.

trans-unit.source: Use LinkedResources to reference .NET Framework resources in satellite assemblies, localized for a particular culture; use the <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.EmbeddedResources%2A> property to embed the resources into the compiled assembly.
trans-unit.target: Bruk LinkedResources til å referere til .NET Framework-ressurser i satelittsamlingene lokalisert for en bestemt kultur. Bruk av <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.EmbeddedResources%2A>egenskapen innebyggingsressurser i kompilerte samlingen.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.EmbeddedResources%2A>

trans-unit.target: En samling som inneholder filbaner for .NET Framework-ressurser som refereres av kilden.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the collection that contains the temporary files.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir samlingen som inneholder de midlertidige filene.

trans-unit.source: The temporary files in the collection are retained or deleted upon the completion of compiler activity based on the value of the <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.TempFileCollection.KeepFiles%2A> property in the collection.
trans-unit.target: De midlertidige filene i samlingen er beholdt eller slettet etter fullføring av kompilatoren aktiviteten basert på verdien for den <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.TempFileCollection.KeepFiles%2A>egenskap i samlingen.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.TempFileCollection.KeepFiles%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.TempFileCollection.KeepFiles%2A> property is set if the collection is created using the <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.TempFileCollection.%23ctor%28System.String%2CSystem.Boolean%29> constructor with the `keepFiles` parameter set to `true`.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.TempFileCollection.KeepFiles%2A>egenskapen angis hvis samlingen opprettes ved hjelp av <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.TempFileCollection.%23ctor%28System.String%2CSystem.Boolean%29>konstruktør med den `keepFiles` parameteren satt til `true`.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.TempFileCollection.%23ctor%28System.String%2CSystem.Boolean%29> </xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.TempFileCollection.KeepFiles%2A>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > This class contains a link demand and an inheritance demand at the class level that applies to all members.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Denne klassen inneholder en kobling behov, og en arv behov på klassen nivå som gjelder for alle medlemmer.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Security.SecurityException> is thrown when either the immediate caller or the derived class does not have full-trust permission.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Security.SecurityException>forårsakes når umiddelbar oppkalleren eller den utledede klassen ikke har tillatelse for fullstendig klarering.</xref:System.Security.SecurityException>

trans-unit.source: For details about security demands, see [Link Demands](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) and [Inheritance Demands](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/28b9adbb-8f08-4f10-b856-dbf59eb932d9).
trans-unit.target: For mer informasjon om krav for sikkerhet, kan du se [koblingen krav](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) og [arv krav](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/28b9adbb-8f08-4f10-b856-dbf59eb932d9).

trans-unit.source: A collection that contains the temporary files.
trans-unit.target: En samling som inneholder de midlertidige filene.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value indicating whether to treat warnings as errors.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om du vil behandle advarsler som feil.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if warnings should be treated as errors; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis advarsler skal behandles som feil. Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the user token to use when creating the compiler process.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir brukertoken skal brukes når du oppretter kompilatoren prosessen.

trans-unit.source: The user token to use.
trans-unit.target: Brukertoken skal brukes.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the warning level at which the compiler aborts compilation.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir advarselsnivået som avbryter kompilatoren kompilering.

trans-unit.source: The warning level at which the compiler aborts compilation.
trans-unit.target: Advarsel nivået som avbryter kompilatoren kompilering.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the file name of a Win32 resource file to link into the compiled assembly.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir navnet på en Win32-ressursfil for å koble til den kompilerte samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Linking files through this property is similar to the `/winres` and `/winresource` command-line arguments supported by many of the .NET Framework compilers.
trans-unit.target: Kobling av filer gjennom denne egenskapen er lik den `/winres` og `/winresource` kommandolinjeargumenter som støttes av mange av .NET Framework-kompilatorer.

trans-unit.source: Use Win32Resource to compile a Win32 resource file into the assembly.
trans-unit.target: Bruk Win32Resource for å kompilere Win32-ressursfil i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Use <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.EmbeddedResources%2A> or <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.LinkedResources%2A> to compile with .NET Framework resource files.
trans-unit.target: Bruk <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.EmbeddedResources%2A>eller <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.LinkedResources%2A>å kompilere med .NET Framework ressursfiler.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.LinkedResources%2A> </xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.EmbeddedResources%2A>

trans-unit.source: Not all compilers support Win32 resource files, so you should test a code generator for this support before linking a resource file by calling the <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.ICodeGenerator.Supports%2A> method with the flag <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.GeneratorSupport>.
trans-unit.target: Ikke alle kompilatorer støtter Win32 ressursfiler, slik at du skal teste en kode generatoren for denne støtten før du kobler en ressursfil ved å kalle <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.ICodeGenerator.Supports%2A>metoden med flagget <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.GeneratorSupport>.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.GeneratorSupport> </xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.ICodeGenerator.Supports%2A>

trans-unit.source: A Win32 resource file that will be linked into the compiled assembly.
trans-unit.target: En Win32-ressursfil som skal knyttes til kompilerte samlingen.
